lead_paragraph: EISENPRESSER--George. We note with sorrow the passing of longtime member, George Eisenpresser, and extend sincerest condolences to his bereaved family. Rabbi Angela W. Buchdahl and President Abigail Pogrebin, Central Synagogue of New York City 1/3
